{"favorite_id": 10127, "calc_type": "", "dosing": false, "full_title_en": "Patient Activity Scale (PAS) for RA", "short_title_en": "Patient Activity Scale for RA", "medium_description_en": "Quantifies severity of rheumatoid arthritis (RA) using patient-reported symptoms.", "short_description_en": "RA severity, more extensive than PAS II.", "before_use": "", "instructions_en": "<p>Note: the <calculator id=\"10128\">PAS II</calculator> is an alternative to the PAS. PAS II uses a slightly different questionnaire with fewer questions than the original PAS, though the overall accuracy of the two is the same.</p>", "purpose_en": ["Prognosis"], "disease_en": ["Rheumatoid Arthritis"], "specialty_en": ["Hospitalist Medicine", "Internal Medicine", "Orthopedics", "Primary Care", "Rheumatology"], "chief_complaint_en": ["Joint Pain"], "system_en": ["Musculoskeletal", "Rheumatologic"], "search_abbreviation_en": ["Disease activity", "pain vas", "haq", "arthritis", "patient global health"], "slug": "patient-activity-scale-pas-ra", "seo": {"meta_description_en": "The Patient Activity Scale (PAS) for RA quantifies severity of rheumatoid arthritis (RA) using patient-reported symptoms.", "keywords_en": "Disease activity, arthritis, patient global health, haq, pain vas"}, "content": {"how_to_use": {"use_case_en": "<p>Do you use the&nbsp;PAS for RA and want to contribute your expertise?&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/join-us\" target=\"_blank\">Join</a>&nbsp;our contributor team!</p>", "pearls_pitfalls_en": "", "why_use_en": ""}, "next_steps": {"advice_en": "<p>Do you use the&nbsp;PAS for RA and want to contribute your expertise?&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/join-us\" target=\"_blank\">Join</a>&nbsp;our contributor team!</p>", "management_en": "", "critical_actions_en": ""}, "about": {"formula_en": "<p dir=\"ltr\">PAS = (A x 3.33 + B + C) / 3, where</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A = Health Assessment Questionnaire Disability Index (HAQ-DI), calculated by averaging of the selected categorical scores* below.</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">B = Pain Visual Analog Scale (ask patient to rate pain on a scale of 0-10, where 10 is worst pain imaginable).</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">C = Patient Global Assessment of Disease Activity (ask patient to rate how well they are doing in the past week considering all the ways their disease affects them on a scale of 0-10, where 10 is the worst).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>*Categorical score is the highest selected score within a given category. Example: If patient can self-dress without any difficulty but shampoos hair with much difficulty, the categorical score for dress and groom&nbsp;is 2.</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"213\" /><col width=\"112\" /><col width=\"124\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Variable</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Points</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to dress and groom</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Self-dress, including shoelaces and buttons</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Shampoo hair</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to a</strong><strong>rise</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Stand up from a straight chair</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Get in and out of bed</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to e</strong><strong>at</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Cut own meat</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Lift a full cup or glass to mouth</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Open a new milk carton</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to w</strong><strong>alk</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Walk outdoors on flat ground</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Climb up five steps</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to p</strong><strong>erform hygiene activities</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Wash and dry body</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Take a tub bath</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Get on and off toilet</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to r</strong><strong>each</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Reach and get down a 5-pound object (such as a bag of sugar) from above head</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Bend down to pick up clothing from floor</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to g</strong><strong>rip</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Open car doors</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Open previously opened jars</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Turn faucets on and off</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Is patient able to p</strong><strong>erform other activities</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Run errands and shop</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Get in and out of car</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Do chores such as vacuuming or yard work</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Without any difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With some difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">1</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With much difficulty</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">2</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Unable</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">3</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If patient uses any aids or devices and/or requires help from another person for any given category, the score for that category is adjusted upward to 2. If the categorical score is already &ge;2, the score remains unchanged.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"></p>", "more_info_en": "<p dir=\"ltr\">Interpretation:</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<table><colgroup><col width=\"*\" /><col width=\"*\" /></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>PAS</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Disease activity</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">0.00-0.25</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Remission</p>\n<